<bibRefCitation id="EFC184B0FFBAC5684275D0C9140DFF78" author="Ibanez-Bernal" box="[832,1283,151,175]" pageId="5" pageNumber="558" refString="Ibanez-Bernal, S. &amp; Hernandez-Ortiz, V. (2010) Ropalomeridae (Ropalomerid flies), pp. 1025 - 1030. In: Brown, B. V. et al. (Eds.). Manual of Central American Diptera, Volume 2. NRC Research Press, Ottawa, Ontario, Canada, 728 pp." type="book chapter" year="2010">
